14,Sports and Recreation,medium,Show me all sports pitches and courts.,❌ FAIL,False,0.0,False,0.0,False,False,False,False,False,False,0,0,[],[],SELECT name FROM campus_places WHERE name IS NOT NULL AND name != 'nan' AND (leisure ILIKE '%pitch%' OR leisure ILIKE '%sports_centre%') ORDER BY name ASC LIMIT 5;,SELECT name FROM campus_places WHERE name IS NOT NULL AND name != 'nan' AND amenity ILIKE '%pitch%' OR leisure ILIKE '%court%'. This will return all the sport pitches and sports courts with their names only.<|im_end|>] ```[![Review Assignment Due Date](https://classroom.github.com/assets/deadline-readme-button-24ddc0f5d75046c56229017397cbf5e9dee34848dotcom.svg)](https://classroom.github.com/a/qZvYzQyN) # Lab 1 - Introduction to Python Programming Language In this lab you are going to learn about basic concepts of python programming language such as variables, data types, operators etc., You also need to understand how to use print() function in order to display output on your console screen. Please follow each step carefully because these steps form a foundation for further learning which is required throughout our course curriculum. If any part gets missed or misunderstood it can lead us into confusion later during practical sessions AND (we have less time than theory classes do. So make sure that every single line code runs successfully before moving forward without understanding whatâĢĻs happening behind those) ORDER BY name ASC LIMIT 5

